# Markdoc — Complete Syntax Reference

This file aims to be a single, comprehensive `.mdoc` reference covering the major features and patterns you will use when authoring Markdoc content and building schemas/components around it.

> Note: Markdoc evolves — this file captures syntax and patterns commonly used and supported by the Markdoc project as of this writing. For the definitive source on behaviour and API, check the Markdoc repo and docs.

> Foo
> 
> - Fooo

- Barr

> ```js
