## 1. Frontmatter (YAML)

Frontmatter appears at the top of the file between `---` markers. It's parsed as YAML and becomes `markdoc.frontmatter`.

```yaml
---
title: "My Fancy Page"
description: "One-line summary."
layout: "docs"
tags:
  - tutorial
  - markdoc
published: true
date: 2025-10-29
authors:
  - name: "Shelton"
    twitter: "@shelton"
version: 1.2
---
````
